ons:<br />\n\t1) the scope of a research<br />\n\t2) widen the scope of the investigation<br />\n\t3) scoping out the venue<br />\n\t4) adjusting the scope on the telescope<br />\n\t5) Instead of writing a scenario, feel free to comment on the story below.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tHe thought he heard the pen roll under his chair, but when he looked, it was not there. So, the interior designer placed all the folders back in the briefcase and got up from the chair. He still did not see his last colored pen. That's strange... he wondered. Closing his briefcase, he placed it down on the chair, and then he started searching. It was getting frustrating when he still did not find it. He shuffled around scoping down. Just when he was about to get down on all four to crawl around, he <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/spot\" target=\"_blank\">spot</a>ted what he was looking for.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/166880147544/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p767192/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p767192\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p766962/\">BBC纪录片《中国新年》全集 附超全笔记精华</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p767427/\">陪跑22年的血泪史！这次咱小李子终于圆满了</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p766914/\">教学：如何和1个美国人展开1段对话</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p767396/\">比尔盖茨2016年度公开信：如果你有种超能力</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p767699/\">奥斯卡红毯：杰克露丝再次合体Gaga仙气十足